## Before Every Session

Ask yourself:
  1. Does this belong in Layer 0, 1, 2, or 3?
  2. Does a file already exist for this domain?
  3. Will this create a new router file? (If yes — justify or absorb)
  4. Will this add to files >500 LOC? (If yes — decompose instead)
  5. Am I in a safety-critical path? (If yes — specific exceptions only)

If you cannot answer all five, stop and re-read PLATFORM_ARCHITECTURE.md.
